usage: 0-1: Left to right; 2: Left + right; 3-127: Right to left
0: Ignore MIDI clock; 1-127: Listen for MIDI clock

0: Thirty-second; 1: Sixteenth; 2: Triplet sixteenth; 3: Eighth; 4: Triplet eighth; 5: Dotted eighth; 6: Quarter; 7: Triplet quarter; 8: Dotted quarter; 9: Half; 10: Dotted half; 11: Whole; 12-127: Double whole
